# Repo-root .dockerignore — applies to any `docker build` invoked with
# the repo root as context (gateway-ingress is the first such image).
# Backend Dockerfile is invoked with `backend/` as context and is
# unaffected.

**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/.vercel
**/coverage
**/.vitest-cache

.git
.github
desktop
e2e
e2b
frontend
cli
backend/.venv
backend/__pycache__
backend/tests
docs
README.md
README_zh.md
LICENSE
SECURITY.md
CONTRIBUTING.md
*.md
!packages/**/README.md
